'''Medisinsk Utdannings og kompetansesenter''' (short form '''MUKS''') is a [[teaching hospital]] located on [[Sessvollmoen]] in central-eastern [[Norway]].
Their main task is to produce medics for different units in the Norwegian defence.

==History==
MUKS was called Sanitetsregimentet until 2002 and was located at Lahaugmoen outside Oslo.

